<view class="wrap">
    <view class="title">收货人
        <text>*</text>
    </view>
    <input class="value" placeholder="请输入真实姓名" placeholder-class="word" bindinput="nameInput"></input>
    <view class="title">手机号码
        <text>*</text>
    </view>
    <input class="value" placeholder="请输入手机号码" placeholder-class="word" bindinput="telInput"></input>
    <view class="title">就读学校
        <text>*</text>
    </view>
    <view class="school">
        <input class="school-value" placeholder="填写学校" placeholder-class="word" bindinput="schoolInput"></input>
        <view class="unselect">
            <picker bindchange="gradeChange" value="{{index}}" range="{{array}}">
                <view>{{array[index]}}</view>
            </picker>
        </view>
    </view>
    <view class="title">充值账号
        <text>*</text>
    </view>
    <input class="value" placeholder="会员账号" placeholder-class="word" bindinput="valueInput"></input>
    <view class="confirm" bindtap="submit">确认</view>
    <view class="intro">一旦确定将无法修改收货地址</view>
    <view class="node-wrap">
        <view class="node-title">友情提示</view>
        <view class="node">1、
            <text>请填写真实的收货地址，一经填写不得修改</text>
        </view>
        <view class="node">2、
            <text>本活动仅面向高三学子，为防止恶意行为，我们将严格审核，不符合条件者将取消领取资格</text>
        </view>
        <view class="node">3、
            <text>兑换提交后，15个工作日之内发货</text>
        </view>
    </view>
</view>